<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Jul1931"><font color="red">13 July 1931</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): In addition to Faber&apos;s offer for <i>W i P</i> (&pound;400 advance of 15% royalties rising to 20%) and Viking Press (&pound;600 of 15% royalties) Harcourt Brace cabled yesterday they would pay &pound;600. As I have to decide within a few days, pending two other American offers and two English ones, will you please let me know your views? Are you interested in publishing the book yourself? </div>
